<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/63726948-tandy-brown">Tandy Brown</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Taliesin is a bit slower than the rest of the books in the series but it does help set the stage for the rest so you can make it through it, it makes <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Taliesin is a bit slower than the rest of the books in the series but it does help set the stage for the rest so you can make it through it, it makes the others more interesting. I did enjoy his Song of Albion series books more than this series so maybe try one of them.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
